					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Oh derring do and knightly deeds! This was as savory as Scotch woodcock and sweet as Nesselrode pudding.</p> <p>The Moon Champion and the Man of La Mancha, showing a valiant newcomer the ways of the Hero - and overcoming the foe. As Marco Polo would say, what need of more words?</p> 
				 	]]>
